name:                callstack
stack:               ( -- a )
return stack:        ( -- )
string stack:        ( -- )
contexts:            stateless
category:            customising

decription:          a variable which determines whether any and what number of call stack
                     items will be displayed in case of an error.
                     The value can be set to an initial value specified in yoda.conf, but
                     also changed any time, by writing the desired value to this variable.

standard:            no
deviation:           standard has no equivalent